<reference id="fig" xml:lang="en-us">
<title><xmlelement>fig</xmlelement></title>
<shortdesc>The <xmlelement>fig</xmlelement> element is a figure (sometimes called an "exhibit")
    with an optional title for a wide variety of content. A figure commonly contains an image or
    artwork, but it can contain several kinds of text objects as well. A title is placed inside the
    figure to provide a caption that describes the content.</shortdesc>
